publications.publisher: INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL FOR INNOVATIVE RESEARCH IN MULTIDISCIPLINARY FIELD
publications.description:
In geospatial domain data structure plays an important role as they are the core component
for analysis. In real life situation, data need to be acquired from various sources and hence
compatibility, standardization of data structure is a limitation.

One instance encountered during a project life-cycle catalyzed our work to find for better and an effective solution, finally paving the way for a nearly neat model.
